title: [1508521049] Nervous Chef Desperate to 'Amaze' Gordon Ramsay | Culinary Genius
description:
The trainee chef can't get his words out. 

Culinary Genius will see nine amateur cooks head into a wrestling ring-style studio to do culinary battle.

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
